description.originalText: Having Jenna as our nanny for a little over two years was a lifesaver for our family. She is reliable, sweet and caring. My twins loved the fun activities that she would plan for them and the attention she would give them. She always made an effort to show us she cared. I highly recommend Jenna as your nanny. My twins still ask how she is doing from time to time which really shows me the impact she had on our family. Thank you Jenna <3

description.displayText: Jenna watched my 1 year old and 3 year old while I worked freelance for 6 months. They loved her. She is very responsible and reliant.

description.displayText:
11/2020-   Jenna was scheduled to begin to babysit for my 8 mo pregnant daughter with 2 toddlers this week.  
Jenna coordinated to begin but said she couldn't start  Monday because she had errands to do.   She then cancelled on the morning of her Tues start day.  She said she was sick, but would start the following day.   My daughter reconfirmed in the evening and Jenna scheduled to start on Wednesday.  On Wed AM,  Jenna sent an email  canceling for Wed.  -again.  Very disappointing.  Very annoying.
Valuable time was wasted with Jenna.   An 8 mo pregnant woman has a very short window to find reliable childcare.   Maybe Jenna  has Covid.  And if so, she should get tested and take down her profile on Care.com.  
No, I would not hire her again.

description.displayText: Jenna is fantastic.  I am sorry to lose her as a regular nanny but we will certainly use her again for babysitting.  My 13 month old, S., loves her to death.  She was great about taking him out to the playground or library everyday and keeping him active and social.  She is easygoing about letting him play and discover but attentive and sent me pictures and made a point of keeping me well-informed of his mood, health, appetite,  etc.

description.displayText: Jenna was able to help us out for a date night on somewhat short notice and did a fantastic job with our three children! They absolutely loved her and gave her a glowing review. She has a great demeanor with kids and pets and was very warm and professional. We'd be delighted to have her take care of our kids again!

description.displayText: Jenna had a great bond with my daughter, who at the time was 5 years old when she babysat her.  Jenna was always on time, and was great with taking my daughter to her activities, reading and playing with her, and prepping a healthy dinner.  I always came to a tidy home with the toys neatly put away.  She's very responsible, loving and kind.  Highly recommend!

description.displayText: I have two special needs children 4 and 5 year's old and from day one Jenna was amazing with them . Always keeping them interested and entertained in all activities. Jenna is a very patient and responsible person always on time and giving her undivided attention to my children. My children love spending time with her and I appreciate her dedicated work ethic.

description.displayText: Jenna kept our little after-school engine running! And with two VERY energetic boys, that's no small thing. She's patient, cheerful, and very conscientious, which means she kept both the parents happy (on time, trustworthy, good communicator) and the kids (fun, crafty, good friend, kind). If our after-school needs hadn't changed, we'd still be working with her!

description.displayText: Jenna babysat for my two girls (ages 4 and 10 months) and they took to her right away. She has no problem corralling/playing with both girls while I got ready for a wedding. My older daughter loved playing with Jenna and the next day told me about the games they played. Jenna had no problems putting my daughter to bed after I left for the night. Jenna was also very understanding when we got home later than we originally planned. I will hire Jenna again when I need a sitter and would recommend her to others.

description.displayText: My husband and I were thrilled with Jenna, but most importantly, our 8 month old daughter loved her. She asked all of the right questions, was comfortable with our baby and our dog, who can be intimidating. She arrived early and texted when our daughter went to bed. I will definitely use her again and highly recommend her!
